# Lynx Bot - Git Ignore

# =============================================================================
# Personal / Sensitive Files (NEVER COMMIT)
# =============================================================================
*.csv
.envrc
gobogoo22.txt
*.txt
!requirements*.txt

# macOS extended attribute files
._*
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Personal analysis / old naming
config/analyze_g22.py
config/history.pretty.json
docs/gabagool-master-plan.md



# =============================================================================
